{% extends 'base.html.j2' %}


{% block main_content %}
<style>
.diwali-gift{
    padding: 30px 0;
}
.diwali-gift .item{
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.gift-subtext{
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 1.5;
  padding-bottom: 0;
  font-family: opensans-regular,Helvetica, sans-serif;
}

.diwali-gift .hollow-button span{
    line-height: 32px;
    padding: 4px 48px;
    display: inline-block;
    margin: 20px 10px 10px;
    border-radius: 30px;
}

.diwali-gift h1{margin-bottom: 20px;}
.diwali-gift .diwali-card{margin-top: 20px;}
.diwali-gift .content{margin-top: 30px;}
.diwali-gift .content h2{font-size: 25px; line-height: 1.4;}
.diwali-gift .content h3{
    font-size: 21px;
    color: #424242;
    font-family: oswald-light;
    font-weight: 500;
}
</style>
<div class="main-content">
  <div class="container corporate-gift diwali-gift">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12 col-xs-12">
        <h1>Gifting Plants for Diwali</h1>
        <p class="gift-subtext">When it comes to Indian festivals, nothing is more mirthful or grand than Diwali. The festival of lights not only marks the Hindu New Year but is also the most dazzling spectacle in India and probably the most anticipated event of the year.</p>
        <p class="gift-subtext">Diwali is one occasion when people come closer, leaving all differences behind and celebrate happiness through the joy of gifting.</p>
        <p class="gift-subtext">Why not redefine gifting, with some novel Diwali gift ideas? Surprise your loved ones with unique Diwali Gifts like these gift plants for Diwali:</p>
      </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12 col-xs-12 diwali-card">
        {% for plant in plants %}
        <div class="item col-md-3 col-xs-12">
         <div class="card">
             <a href="{{ url('plant_details', args=[plant.slug]) }}">
             <div class="slider-image">
               {% if plant.images.all()|length>0 %}
                 <img src="/media/{{ plant.images.all()[0].image }}" alt="{{ plant.images.all()[0].alt }}" title="{{ plant.images.all()[0].title }}">
               {% endif %}
             </div>
             <div class="sale-new">
                     <h6 class="text">New</h6>
             </div>
           </a>
             <div class="heart">
                 <i class="fa fa-heart-o"></i>
             </div>
             <div class="content">
                 <a href="{{ url('plant_details', args=[plant.slug]) }}">
                 <h6 class="title">{{plant.name}}</h6>
                 <h6 class="price"><i class="fa fa-inr"></i> {{plant.actual_price}}</h6>
                 <h6 class="price active-price"><i class="fa fa-inr"></i> {{plant.selling_price}}</h6>
                 </a>
                 <div class="hollow-button">
                   {% if plant.stock %}
                     <a id="ga-gd-tracking" onclick="add_to_cart({{plant.id}},1)" class="button ga-gd-tracking"><i class="fa fa-shopping-cart"></i> Add To Cart</a>
                   {% else %}
                     <span class="button no-stock-btn ">Out of Stock</span>
                   {% endif %}
                 </div>
             </div>
         </div>
         </div>
         {% endfor %}

     </div>
    </div>

     <div class="row">
       <div class="col-md-12 col-xs-12">

         <div class="content">
          <h2>Why consider a plant as gift on Diwali?</h2>
          <p class="gift-subtext">Gifting natural plants is already a cultural phenomenon across Europe, Asia and America. Plants are natural stress busters and help create a friendly and positive environment. By gifting plants for Diwali, you are not only sending your heartfelt wishes to your loved ones but also spreading prosperity and good fortune and awareness about the environment too!</p>
          <p class="gift-subtext">At Green Decor, we offer a range of Diwali gift plants that are non-toxic, low maintenance and work perfectly to uplift your mood with their calming presence and natural beauty.</p>
        </div>

         <div class="content">
          <h2>Corporate Gift Plants for Diwali</h2>
          <p class="gift-subtext">Diwali is all about spreading happiness and love. Therefore, as a business owner, you would surely want to share your joy with the staff members. What better way to share joy than giving them plants for Diwali gifts? Your employees will love the unique and meaningful gesture, and come back to work with renewed enthusiasm.</p>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-xs-12">
                  <h3>Best Diwali Gift for Employees</h3>
                  <p class="gift-subtext">At Green Decor, you can choose from a range of beautiful ferns such as Boston Fern, Asplenium Nidus, and Foxtail Fern, along with other exciting options including bonsai and succulents. These plants are available in various patterns and arrangements and can be customised to suit your needs.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-12 col-xs-12">
                  <h3>Diwali Gifts for Clients</h3>
                  <p class="gift-subtext">Just like your employees, your clients too deserve a personalised commitment on your part. Diwali is a great occasion for you to appreciate your clients through gifts that are meaningful and convey your sincerity. All the more reason to consider indoor plants as Diwali gifts for clients as the long lasting air purifier and will act as a symbol of long term relationship. Green Decor brings you an eclectic collection of flowering plants, aromatic indoor plant varieties and money magnet.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-12 col-xs-12">
                  <h3>Diwali Gifts for Family</h3>
                  <p class="gift-subtext">Your family is perhaps your most significant achievement in life. And like everyone else, they too deserve to know that you care for them. This Diwali season, show your devotion and undying love for your family through indoor plants that are long lasting yet spectacularly beautiful. Therefore, be imaginative and add value to your expressions through insightful Diwali plant gifts.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
        </div>

         <div class="content">
          <h2>Exploring the World of Unique Diwali Gifts at Green Decor</h2>
          <p class="gift-subtext">Green Decor is your one-stop solution to buy exciting Diwali gifts online for your family, employees and clients. You can find an array of unique Diwali gift plants - a collection you won’t see anyplace else. What’s more?</p>
          <p class="gift-subtext">With a simple mouse button click, you can send a customised collection of beautiful indoor plants to your employees, clients or family members, anywhere in India. Moreover, our logistics team is equipped to deliver your gifts promptly and timely. Therefore, leave all the worries behind, visit greendecor. in, select your favourite Diwali plant gift, and we’ll take it from there.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>


  </div>
</div>
{% endblock %}
